title: The End Times, The Final Chapter of GD.
body:
#Latest Installment (Boards Feedback: Completed)
http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/GD/MbHPFq2g-the-end-times-the-final-chapter-of-gd?show=flat&comment=00cc
---

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ql8K3KJyWgY
http://puu.sh/iugW8/33e3ab6b52.jpg Is everything in place, Dillon?
http://puu.sh/iugZY/fa1f8e6680.jpg Of course, master Wookiecookie.
http://puu.sh/iugW8/33e3ab6b52.jpg Excellent. Make the post.
*Dillon hits the large "Post Discussion" button.*
http://puu.sh/iuh3q/c9f8031199.png
http://puu.sh/iugW8/33e3ab6b52.jpg Good, now we wait.

*Meanwhile...*
http://puu.sh/iuh5Q/ae3f831123.jpg
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqYkP8Hp4Lw
http://puu.sh/iuhgi/7ba86cf1cd.jpg Did you see it?
http://puu.sh/iuhdP/8f7b992dc7.jpg Aye.
http://puu.sh/iugQp/d479ed6b94.jpg What do you propose we do?
http://puu.sh/iuhgi/7ba86cf1cd.jpg I don't think there's anything we **can** do...
http://puu.sh/iuhj0/bc227b783f.jpg No, we'll do what we always do.
http://puu.sh/iugQp/d479ed6b94.jpg Try to take over the world?
http://puu.sh/iuhj0/bc227b783f.jpg Think smaller scale.
http://puu.sh/iuhv8/99d2fd012b.jpg I'm in this story too.
http://puu.sh/iuhgi/7ba86cf1cd.jpg Try to make Riot see logic and reason?
http://puu.sh/iuhdP/8f7b992dc7.jpg That never works, but it's always worth a shot.
http://puu.sh/iuhj0/bc227b783f.jpg Agreed, let's see what we can do.
*And so our group set off, heading out to see what they could do to stop the evil Wookiecookie and his henchman, ADillonMostDirty*

*To be Continued...*
